details.name: Chaotic Offering
details.description: Summons a Golem from the depths, stunning enemies for one second. The Golem lives 60 seconds, takes reduced damage from spells, has Permanent Immolation and Flaming Fists on attack. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Calls 2 Golems with reduced stats and bounty.
